クラス TextDifferToHTML

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kazurayam.materialstore.reduce.differ.AbstractTextDiffer
      • com.kazurayam.materialstore.reduce.differ.TextDifferToHTML
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    Differ, HTMLPrettyPrintingCapable

    public final class TextDifferToHTML
extends AbstractTextDiffer
implements Differ, HTMLPrettyPrintingCapable
    compiles a HTML report of diff of 2 text files presents the diff information in a HTML like the GitHub History split view.

    uses java-diff-utils on GitHub https://github.com/java-diff-utils/java-diff-utils to make diff of 2 texts
